{
  "stem": "5496.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then he said, look, it's OK with me, but I think you ought to go and have special schooling for it so you can be licensed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he's the one who urged me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And indeed, I did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I became a licensed x-ray technician and surgical assistant in there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I seemed to have somehow found a group of young people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of them were also survivors, and I had contact with them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was barely in New York when I met Fred.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if I may, I must tell this story, because this is one for the books.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the meantime, my uncle came out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This doctor, as I said, was a kidney specialist, and my uncle had a serious kidney problem and the doctor had to operate on him, I'm happy to say, successfully.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And his one and only daughter Margaret, my cousin, was so grateful that we took such good care of him, of course special care and all that, that after he got well-- she worked for a ring casting company-- she wanted to give me something.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And since I didn't have a thing, she brought home a number of rings.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I say, you pick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One was a little pearl, one was a green stone, one, whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You pick whatever you like.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, I chose garnet, which is a Czech stone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the reason why I'm saying that it's so important, had I not chosen this, I would have never met Fred, because after I saved up $15, I was anxious to get a pair of matching earrings.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And somebody told me that a man from Czechoslovakia, who, indeed, I know-- knew his wife and him from Italy, they have an import business on garnets on 47th Street.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
